fields.title: Building a Modern Web App from Scratch
fields.description: In this comprehensive tutorial, we'll build a modern web application from scratch using React, TypeScript, and Vite. Learn best practices, project structure, and advanced patterns.
fields.transcript:
Video Transcript

00:00 - Introduction

Hello everyone! Today we're going to build a modern web application from scratch.

02:15 - Project Setup

First, let's create a new project using Vite and configure TypeScript.

05:30 - Component Architecture

Now, let's discuss how to structure our components for maximum reusability.

10:45 - State Management

We'll implement state management using React Query and Zustand.

15:00 - Styling and UI

Let's add some beautiful styles using Tailwind CSS and custom components.

fields.title: Advanced TypeScript Patterns
fields.description: Dive deep into advanced TypeScript patterns and techniques. Learn about generics, conditional types, mapped types, and more.
